name: Hypixel AutoWoot
body:
# General Information:
The Hypixel AutoWoot is a script used to automatically woot songs that are being played. It's easy to use and easy to set up.

**To toggle the AutoWoot script just double click on the woot button**

# Installation:
Installation is very easy, simply drag the link below to your bookmark bar.
[Drag Me](javascript: (function (){var jsCode = document.createElement('script'); jsCode.setAttribute('id', 'HypixelBot'); jsCode.setAttribute('src', 'https://raw.github.com/xmannj2/HypixelBot/master/Bot.js'); document.body.appendChild(jsCode); }());)

or you could manually add this url to your bookmarks:
```
javascript: (function (){var jsCode = document.createElement('script'); jsCode.setAttribute('id', 'HypixelBot'); jsCode.setAttribute('src', 'https://raw.github.com/xmannj2/HypixelBot/master/Bot.js'); document.body.appendChild(jsCode); }());
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
